Running the Bot
Development/Live Trading:

Bash

npm start
(You'll define start script in package.json to run index.js)

Paper Trading:
Set MODE=paper in .env and run:

Bash

npm start
Backtesting:
Set MODE=backtest in .env, configure BACKTEST_START_DATE, BACKTEST_END_DATE, BACKTEST_SYMBOL, BACKTEST_TIMEFRAME and ensure you have historical data in data/. Then run:

Bash

npm start